## ğŸ“‹ IMPLEMENTATION ROADMAP (4 WEEKS)

### WEEK 1: Foundation & Authentication
**Estimated: 40 hours**

**Day 1: Database Models**
- [ ] Create `models/user.py` - User, Session, AuditLog
- [ ] Create `models/candidate.py` - Candidate profile
- [ ] Create `models/job.py` - Job posting
- [ ] Create `models/match.py` - Job-candidate matching
- [ ] Setup SQLAlchemy ORM
- [ ] Create database migrations

**Day 2: Authentication API**
- [ ] `POST /api/auth/register` - User registration
- [ ] `POST /api/auth/login` - User login with JWT
- [ ] `POST /api/auth/refresh` - Refresh tokens
- [ ] `POST /api/auth/logout` - Logout & revoke session
- [ ] `GET /api/auth/me` - Get current user
- [ ] Email verification system

**Day 3: Protected Routes**
- [ ] JWT middleware setup
- [ ] Role-based access control (RBAC)
- [ ] Private route protection
- [ ] Error handling

**Day 4-5: Testing & Integration**
- [ ] Unit tests for auth endpoints
- [ ] Integration tests with database
- [ ] API documentation with Swagger
- [ ] Bug fixes & optimization

**Deliverable**: Secure authentication system, all auth endpoints tested

---

### WEEK 2: CRUD Operations & Core Features
**Estimated: 50 hours**

**Day 1-2: Candidates CRUD**
- [ ] `GET /api/candidates` - List all candidates
- [ ] `POST /api/candidates` - Create candidate
- [ ] `GET /api/candidates/{id}` - Get candidate details
- [ ] `PUT /api/candidates/{id}` - Update candidate
- [ ] `DELETE /api/candidates/{id}` - Delete candidate
- [ ] Resume upload and parsing
- [ ] Skill extraction from resume

**Day 3-4: Jobs CRUD**
- [ ] `GET /api/jobs` - List all jobs
- [ ] `POST /api/jobs` - Create job posting
- [ ] `GET /api/jobs/{id}` - Get job details
- [ ] `PUT /api/jobs/{id}` - Update job
- [ ] `DELETE /api/jobs/{id}` - Close/delete job
- [ ] Job search & filtering
- [ ] Salary range analysis

**Day 5: Matching Algorithm**
- [ ] AI scoring engine
- [ ] Skill match calculation
- [ ] Experience level matching
- [ ] Salary fit analysis
- [ ] `POST /api/matches/calculate` - Trigger matching
- [ ] Match persistence

**Deliverable**: Full CRUD operations, AI matching algorithm working

