## ğŸ“ API ENDPOINTS (Complete List)

### Authentication
```
POST   /api/auth/register       - Register new user
POST   /api/auth/login          - User login
POST   /api/auth/logout         - Logout
POST   /api/auth/refresh        - Refresh JWT
GET    /api/auth/me             - Current user
PUT    /api/auth/me             - Update profile
```

### Candidates
```
GET    /api/candidates          - List candidates
POST   /api/candidates          - Create candidate
GET    /api/candidates/{id}     - Get candidate
PUT    /api/candidates/{id}     - Update candidate
DELETE /api/candidates/{id}     - Delete candidate
POST   /api/candidates/upload   - Upload resume
```

### Jobs
```
GET    /api/jobs                - List jobs
POST   /api/jobs                - Post job
GET    /api/jobs/{id}           - Get job details
PUT    /api/jobs/{id}           - Update job
DELETE /api/jobs/{id}           - Close job
```

### Matching & AI
```
GET    /api/matches             - List matches
POST   /api/matches/calculate   - Run matching algorithm
GET    /api/matches/job/{jobId} - Get job matches
PUT    /api/matches/{id}/status - Update match status
```

### Admin
```
GET    /api/admin/stats         - Platform statistics
GET    /api/admin/users         - Manage users
GET    /api/admin/audit-logs    - Audit trail
```

